review_blob: When io tried this i was took back by the quality the taste was out of this world. A real ale for real people.

I tried this beer once and it changed me from Larger to bitter at once. A very fruity, hoppy little number that has a rather special malty finish much like the Old Horny bitter from the same brewer. A must try...
This particular larger was named after a well known local serial killer!

This brewery has also just launched thier Web site at www.blythebrewery.co.uk
Chase Bitter is well known not to the masses but to a few hundred people who like us are lucky enough to have it on tap. If you get the chance try it an amazing bitter!
